$ chexa8_cantilever_modal.bdf
$ Cantilever bar: 5x2x2 CHEXA8, L=1m, a=0.01m square cross-section
$ E=200 GPa, rho=7850 kg/m^3
$
$ Analytical first bending (Euler-Bernoulli cantilever):
$   f1 = 1.8751^2 * sqrt(EI/rhoA) / (2*pi*L^2)
$   I = a^4/12 = 8.333e-10 m^4,  A = a^2 = 1e-4 m^2
$   EI/rhoA = 212.3 m^4/s^2  =>  f1 = 8.15 Hz
$   Modes 1 and 2 are degenerate (bending in Y and Z planes).
SOL 103
CEND
SUBCASE 1
  LABEL = CHEXA8 CANTILEVER MODAL
  SPC = 1
  METHOD = 1
  EIGENVECTOR(PLOT) = ALL
